text: On the latest #TWiV Daniel Griffin's #COVID19 clinical report, Bill Foege’s letter to CDC director Redfield, false promise of herd immunity, secret blueprints for #SARSCoV2 vaccine trials released, neuropilin-1 as possible entry protein for the virus https://t.co/ro4yhZJe5Q https://t.co/5BJKUrYnri

On the latest #TWiV Daniel Griffin #COVID19 report, debunking Great Barrington Declaration, smell and taste changes early indicators of pandemic, vascular disease and thrombosis in infected humans and macaques, swine pathogen SADS-CoV infects human cells https://t.co/AfqnNlWygn https://t.co/6RHaefvfh8

On the latest #TWiV a #COVID19 clinical report from Daniel Griffin, AmyVirologist @abr22 joins us to discuss 2020 Chemistry Nobel Prize for gene editing, circulation of poliovirus in Afghanistan, inborn errors of interferon in severe COVID-19 https://t.co/OtGIZGjjNV https://t.co/lwD7hhOSs9

On the latest #TWiV Kizzmekia Corbett joins to review her work on respiratory syncytial virus, influenza virus, coronaviruses and coronavirus vaccines, development and testing of spike mRNA vaccine, and the Nobel Prize for discovery of hepatitis C virus https://t.co/QkFJVVVVET https://t.co/TziWfwrq4w
